These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, librarian
1. the engineer is on the far left##1
2. the bartender is on the right of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | engineer | librarian | bartender |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, doctor, photographer
1. the photographer is on the far right##1
2. the dancer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | dancer | doctor | photographer |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, reading, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | baking | reading | video-games |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: french, japanese, nigerian
1. the japanese is on the far right##1
2. the japanese is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | french | nigerian | japanese |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, water
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | sprite | almond-milk | water |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, car, snowmobile
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car | boat |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, martial-arts, thriller
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | action | martial-arts |

 #################################
 
